## 📋 WORKSHEET STRUCTURE

### **📊 Sheet 1: Project Overview**
```
Green Africa Hub - R&D Consultancy Analytics
AI-Powered Sustainable Innovation Intelligence

PROJECT DETAILS:
- Project ID: [AUTO-GENERATED]
- Client Name: [TEXT]
- Project Type: [DROPDOWN: Recipe Optimization/Kitchen Efficiency/Product Development/Process Improvement]
- Start Date: [DATE PICKER]
- End Date: [DATE PICKER]
- Research Focus: [DROPDOWN: Carbon Reduction/Cost Savings/Cultural Preservation/Energy Efficiency]
- Budget: [CURRENCY]

AI CALCULATED METRICS:
- Innovation Potential Score: [AI SCORE 1-100]
- Sustainability Impact: [AI RATING A-F]
- Cultural Preservation Value: [AI SCORE 1-10]
- Commercial Viability: [AI PERCENTAGE]
- Research ROI Projection: [AI PERCENTAGE]
```

### **📊 Sheet 2: Research Data**
```
EXPERIMENTAL TRACKING:
Experiment ID | Date | Objective | Method | Variables | Results | Success Rate | AI Analysis

RESEARCH METRICS:
- Hypothesis Validation: [INPUT] | [AI VALIDATION] | [CONFIDENCE SCORE]
- Experimental Success: [INPUT] | [AI ANALYSIS] | [PREDICTION]
- Data Quality Score: [AI CALCULATION] | [IMPROVEMENT NEEDED]
- Reproducibility Rate: [AI ASSESSMENT] | [RELIABILITY SCORE]

AI RESEARCH INSIGHTS:
- Research Efficiency: =AI_RESEARCH_EFFICIENCY()
- Innovation Index: =AI_INNOVATION_SCORE()
- Data Pattern Recognition: =AI_PATTERN_ANALYSIS()
- Future Research Direction: =AI_RESEARCH_PREDICTION()
```

### **📊 Sheet 3: Sustainability Analysis**
```
