- Packaging Waste (kg): [BASELINE] | [OPTIMIZED] | [REDUCTION] | [AI SUGGESTIONS]
- Resource Efficiency: [BASELINE] | [OPTIMIZED] | [IMPROVEMENT] | [AI ANALYSIS]

AI SUSTAINABILITY METRICS:
- Overall Sustainability Score: =AI_SUSTAINABILITY_SCORE()
- Environmental Impact Rating: =AI_ENVIRONMENTAL_RATING()
- Carbon Reduction Potential: =AI_CARBON_POTENTIAL()
