## 🤖 AI FORMULAS & FUNCTIONS

### **Research Analysis AI:**
```excel
=AI_RESEARCH_EFFICIENCY(experiment_data, time_investment, resource_usage)
=AI_INNOVATION_SCORE(novelty, feasibility, market_potential)
=AI_PATTERN_ANALYSIS(research_data, historical_patterns, future_trends)
=AI_RESEARCH_PREDICTION(current_findings, success_probability, timeline)
```

### **Sustainability AI:**
```excel
=AI_SUSTAINABILITY_SCORE(carbon_data, waste_reduction, energy_efficiency)
=AI_ENVIRONMENTAL_RATING(impact_metrics, industry_benchmarks, regulations)
=AI_CARBON_POTENTIAL(current_emissions, reduction_techniques, scalability)
=AI_CIRCULAR_ECONOMY(resource_usage, waste_recycling, sustainability_metrics)
```

### **Cultural Adaptation AI:**
```excel
=AI_CULTURAL_SUSTAINABILITY(traditional_methods, sustainable_adaptations, community_feedback)
=AI_HERITAGE_PRESERVATION(authenticity_score, cultural_significance, preservation_methods)
=AI_COMMUNITY_ACCEPTANCE(cultural_relevance, heritage_value, community_demographics)
=AI_CULTURAL_INNOVATION(tradition_balance, innovation_level, acceptance_prediction)
```

### **Business Impact AI:**
```excel
=AI_FINANCIAL_IMPACT(cost_savings, revenue_potential, market_size)
=AI_MARKET_OPPORTUNITY(competitive_landscape, market_trends, growth_potential)
=AI_COMPETITIVE_EDGE(innovation_level, sustainability_advantage, cultural_authenticity)
=AI_SCALABILITY_INDEX(current_model, expansion_potential, resource_requirements)
```

